  "description_of_services":[
    "The Law Department supervises approximately 60 attorneys citywide. The Department also directly supervises approximately 25 support staff employees who work with the legal staff. The Department is responsible for handling court litigation, administrative hearings, appellate reviews, advisory opinions/memoranda, drafting and approving legal instruments, drafting and analyzing legislation, and providing general legal counsel."
